Clement's law firm, Bancroft PLLC, was one of nearly two dozen firms that helped sponsor the annual dinner of the Federalist Society, a long-standing group that has consistently championed conservative legal principles.
The other firm that sponsored the lunch is one of the trade associations that challenged the law, the National Federation of Independent Business.
