The water main will be 3D with Super Mario 3D Land.
Super Mario has fought tirelessly for over 25 years to save Princess Peach from Bowser's evil clutches, but he's never done it in three dimensions before: in Super Mario 3D Land, he'll fight for a girl's love in stereoscopic technology.
